com.xilinx.rapidwright.device

Class BEL

  • Object
    • com.xilinx.rapidwright.device.BooleanFlagHelper
      • com.xilinx.rapidwright.device.BEL

  • public class BEL
extends BooleanFlagHelper
    This class represents the canonical representation of a BEL (Basic Element of Logic), or a RBEL (Routing BEL), or a site port. These are the indivisible elements present in a site. Created on: Oct 1, 2015
